Chelsea hasn&rsquo;t announced Laurent Blanc, the plan b, simply because Maurizio Sarri remain at the top of the list. He&rsquo;s stil there from many weeks. We told you that starting from monday it would be hot days. So: tomorrow could be the crucial day with a meeting dedicated to the manager affair, ascertained that Conte &ndash; despite a milionaire contract &ndash; has no more approval from the club. Chelsea will perfect to Sarri the proposal made a many weeks ago. It should pass to the operative phase. That is a three years contract or a two years plus option. It&rsquo;s possible a contact with Napoli, since the clause has expired at the end of may (the 31st&hellip;), for an agreement that can open up transfers prospects. David Luiz for Ancelotti? It is an idea. Chelsea, of the eventually new course, likes Hysaj (50 milion euros clause), Albiol (6 milion euros clause) and Higuain (no more untuchable at Juventus, in a transaction that could allow Morata to take the reverse path). But  first of all the terms of the agreement between Sarri and Chelsea, between prudence and expectation. Tomorrow we will know more, after many weeks lived on razor&rsquo;s edge.<br />
<br />
@AlfredoPedulla
